  "body": "# Feature\r\n\r\nDesigners recently (Mar 15, 2023) updated Figma with the correct colors for the unread Activity Center indicator in all states. Actually **dark mode is still in progress**. We should match what's in Figma.\r\n\r\nAnother important change is that we should display an unread dot, i.e. **without** a counter.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/46027/225418072-6cbf3221-e8f7-4f65-b507-94fe5e422f4b.png)\r\n\r\n### References\r\n\r\nFigma - Shell for Mobile: https://www.figma.com/file/eDfxTa9IoaCMUy5cLTp0ys/Shell-for-Mobile?node-id=5305%3A521993&t=X4SBEJrRA8Bdvl4q-0\r\n",
